  "details": "XZ Utils is an integrated collection of user-space file compression utilities based on the Lempel-Ziv-Markov chain algorithm (LZMA), which performs lossless data compression. The algorithm provides a high compression ratio while keeping the decompression time short.  \n\nSecurity Fix(es):  \n\n  * xz: XZ has a heap-use-after-free bug in threaded .xz decoder (CVE-2025-31115)\n\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n",
